        <body>
            
            
            <div xml:id="May"> 
                <interpGrp type="poembox">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="may"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="leaves"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="fall"></interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <lg> 
                    
            
                    <l>The wind is tossing the lilacs,</l>
                    <l> The new leaves laugh in the sun,</l>
                    <l> And the petals fall on the orchard wall,</l>
                    <l> But for me the spring is done.</l>
            
                    <l> Beneath the apple blossoms,</l>
                    <l>I go a wintry way,,</l>
                    <l> For love that smiled in April,</l>
                    <l> Is false to me in May.,</l>
            
                    <l>Source: https://www.familyfriendpoems.com/poem/may-by-sara-teasdale,</l>
                    
